lead_paragraph: Swansea City manager Bob Bradley does not blame the fans for booing his team off at halftime after watching them fall three goals behind a visiting Manchester United inside 33 minutes at the Liberty Stadium on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Fans Have Every Right to Be Angry, Says Swansea's Bradley
